Detailed Description

cvmx_sli_pp_pkt_csr_control

This register provides access to SLI packet register space from the cores. These SLI packet registers include the following: SLI_MSIXX_TABLE_ADDR, SLI_MSIXX_TABLE_DATA, SLI_MSIX_PBA0, SLI_MSIX_PBA1, SLI_PKTX_INPUT_CONTROL, SLI_PKTX_INSTR_BADDR, SLI_PKTX_INSTR_BAOFF_DBELL, SLI_PKTX_INSTR_FIFO_RSIZE, SLI_PKT_IN_DONEX_CNTS, SLI_PKTX_OUTPUT_CONTROL, SLI_PKTX_OUT_SIZE, SLI_PKTX_SLIST_BADDR, SLI_PKTX_SLIST_BAOFF_DBELL, SLI_PKTX_SLIST_FIFO_RSIZE, SLI_PKTX_INT_LEVELS, SLI_PKTX_CNTS, SLI_PKTX_ERROR_INFO, SLI_PKTX_VF_INT_SUM, SLI_PKTX_PF_VF_MBOX_SIG, SLI_PKTX_MBOX_INT.
